:children.description: The children to render as the navbar menu. Usually a list of `NavbarMenuItem` components.
:children.description_zh: 要呈现为导航栏菜单的子项。通常是“NavbarMenuItem”组件的列表。

portalContainer.description: The container element in which the navbar menu overlay portal will be placed.
portalContainer.description_zh: 将在其中放置导航栏菜单覆盖门户的容器元素。

:motionProps.description: The motion props to controle the `open` / `close` animation. This motion is only available if the `disableAnimation` prop is set to false.
:motionProps.description_zh: 用于控制“打开”/“关闭”动画的运动道具。仅当“disableAnimation”道具设置为“false”时，此动作才可用。
